'''中國－伊拉克關係'''（{{lang-ar|العلاقات العراقية الصينية}}）是指[[中國|中國]]和[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]之間的[[外交關係|外交關係]]。

==歷史==
[[File:Iraqi_Embassy_in_Beijing.JPG|thumb]]

1942年3月16日，中华民国与伊拉克王国簽署《中華民國[[伊拉克王國|伊拉克王國]]友好條約》，建立公使級[[外交#外交上的承認|外交關係]]。<ref name="條約協定">{{Cite web |url = http://no06.mofa.gov.tw/mofatreatys/Result.aspx?tysubject_c=&tysubject_e=&tysubject_o=&tycountry_c=%e4%bc%8a%e6%8b%89%e5%85%8b&tycountry_e=%e4%bc%8a%e6%8b%89%e5%85%8b&tyeffectivedate=&tyeffectivedateE=&tysigneddate=&tysigneddateE=&start=Y&tykeyword=&Order=Signing |title = 條約協定查詢系統 |publisher = 中華民國外交部 |accessdate = 2020-03-03 |archive-date = 2019-05-11 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190511154146/http://no06.mofa.gov.tw/mofatreatys/Result.aspx?tysubject_c=&tysubject_e=&tysubject_o=&tycountry_c=%e4%bc%8a%e6%8b%89%e5%85%8b&tycountry_e=%e4%bc%8a%e6%8b%89%e5%85%8b&tyeffectivedate=&tyeffectivedateE=&tysigneddate=&tysigneddateE=&start=Y&tykeyword=&Order=Signing |dead-url = no }}</ref>到1949年中华人民共和国成立后，伊拉克王国继续与中华民国维持外交关系，1957年，伊拉克王储[[阿布杜勒·伊拉|阿布杜勒·伊拉]]访问中華民國。1958年伊拉克爆发[[1958年伊拉克革命|革命]]，推翻了[[哈希姆王朝|哈希姆王朝]]，之后新的伊拉克政府和中华人民共和国于1958年8月25日建交。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.holyland-inc.net/me-arab-crude-oil/China-ME.htm |title=Energy First - China and the Middle East dictated by her thirst for oil |accessdate=2015-03-24 |archive-date=2009-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091213230637/http://www.holyland-inc.net/me-arab-crude-oil/China-ME.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>1960年代期間，伊拉克在[[六日戰爭|六日戰爭]]和[[贖罪日戰爭|贖罪日戰爭]]與[[以色列|以色列]]交戰時購買前[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]和中國的武器，使兩國關係變得更親密。

1971年伊拉克支持[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]]恢復在[[聯合國|聯合國]]的席位。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/baltsun/offers.html?url=%2Fbaltsun%2Faccess%2F1751655122.html%3FFMT%3DAI%26type%3Dhistoric%26date%3DJul%2B19%252C%2B1971%26author%3D%26pub%3DThe%2BSun%2B(1837-1985)%26desc%3DPeking%2BBacks%2BPlan%2BTo%2BGive%2BIt%2BU.N.%2BSeat |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-03-24 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402103157/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/baltsun/offers.html?url=%2Fbaltsun%2Faccess%2F1751655122.html%3FFMT%3DAI%26type%3Dhistoric%26date%3DJul%2B19%252C%2B1971%26author%3D%26pub%3DThe%2BSun%2B%281837-1985%29%26desc%3DPeking%2BBacks%2BPlan%2BTo%2BGive%2BIt%2BU.N.%2BSeat |dead-url=no }}</ref>1980年代[[兩伊戰爭|兩伊戰爭]]期間，中國對雙方都是重要的支持者。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=8f8gAAAAIBAJ&sjid=2HQFAAAAIBAJ&pg=1407,4501649&dq=china+iraq+relations+history&hl=en |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-03-24 |archive-date=2020-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715013243/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=8f8gAAAAIBAJ&sjid=2HQFAAAAIBAJ&pg=1407,4501649&dq=china+iraq+relations+history&hl=en }}</ref>

1991年[[波斯灣戰爭|波斯灣戰爭]]期間中國曾經讉責伊拉克入侵[[科威特|科威特]]，後來[[美國政府|美國政府]]称其發現中國違反聯合國對波斯灣戰爭的協議。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/chicagotribune/access/24714227.html?dids=24714227:24714227&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=May+07%2C+1991&author=Uli+Schmetzer%2C+Chicago+Tribune.&pub=Chicago+Tribune+(pre-1997+Fulltext)&desc=U.S.+to+China%3A+Improve+human+rights+to+mend+ties&pqatl=google |title=U.S. to China: Improve human rights to mend ties |accessdate=2015-03-24 |archive-date=2012-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103184150/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/chicagotribune/access/24714227.html?dids=24714227:24714227&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=May+07,+1991&author=Uli+Schmetzer,+Chicago+Tribune.&pub=Chicago+Tribune+(pre-1997+Fulltext)&desc=U.S.+to+China:+Improve+human+rights+to+mend+ties&pqatl=google |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 雙邊關係 ==
[[中國|中國]]強烈反對2003年[[伊拉克戰爭|伊拉克戰爭]]，並且連同[[法國|法國]]、[[德國|德國]]以及[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]強烈譴責美國入侵及佔領的行為，要求美國從伊拉克撤軍。四國都反對英美的決定，並且在聯合國要求外的情況下拒絕派出人員參與。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.peopledaily.com.cn/200304/04/eng20030404_114559.shtml |title=Commentary: Will the World Pattern Change? |accessdate=2015-03-24 |archive-date=2012-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012112601/http://english.peopledaily.com.cn/200304/04/eng20030404_114559.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>中國和俄羅斯公司成為伊拉克石油的最大贏家。中國公司按合約願意營運20年，比西方社會的公司提供較低利潤<ref name=at-20091216>{{cite news |url=http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Middle_East/KL16Ak02.html |title=Iraq's oil auction hits the jackpot |author=Pepe Escobar |newspaper=Asia Times |date=16 December 2009 |accessdate=20 August 2014 |archive-date=2015-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150316131325/http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Middle_East/KL16Ak02.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年，中國購買接近一半伊拉克石油產品，將近每日150萬桶。<ref name=nyt-20130602>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/03/world/middleeast/china-reaps-biggest-benefits-of-iraq-oil-boom.html |title=China Is Reaping Biggest Benefits of Iraq Oil Boom |author=Tim Arango and Clifford Krauss |newspaper=New York Times |date=2 June 2013 |accessdate=20 August 2014 |archive-date=2015-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403094438/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/03/world/middleeast/china-reaps-biggest-benefits-of-iraq-oil-boom.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

